# UI Component Patterns

## Component Library
- **shadcn/ui**: Primary component library
- **Tailwind CSS**: Styling framework
- **Lucide React**: Icon library

## Key Components
- **Dashboard**: [src/components/Dashboard.tsx](mdc:src/components/Dashboard.tsx) - Main dashboard view
- **FileUpload**: [src/components/FileUpload.tsx](mdc:src/components/FileUpload.tsx) - File upload interface
- **Navbar**: [src/components/Navbar.tsx](mdc:src/components/Navbar.tsx) - Navigation bar
- **DynamicKPISection**: [src/components/DynamicKPISection.tsx](mdc:src/components/DynamicKPISection.tsx) - KPI cards
- **GameTables**: [src/components/GameTables.tsx](mdc:src/components/GameTables.tsx) - Game-specific tables

## Layout Patterns
1. **Accordion Layout**: Use expandable sections instead of grid cards
2. **Responsive Design**: Mobile-first approach with Tailwind breakpoints
3. **Dark/Light Theme**: Implemented via [ThemeContext.tsx](mdc:src/contexts/ThemeContext.tsx)
4. **Turkish Localization**: All UI text in Turkish

## Styling Guidelines
- Use Tailwind utility classes
- Follow shadcn/ui component patterns
- Maintain consistent spacing and typography
- Use semantic color names (e.g., `text-primary`, `bg-secondary`)
- Implement hover states and transitions

## Component Structure
```typescript
// Example component structure
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"
import { Card } from "@/components/ui/card"

export function MyComponent() {
  return (
    <Card className="p-4">
      <h3 className="text-lg font-semibold">Title</h3>
      <Button variant="default">Action</Button>
    </Card>
  )
}
```
